title: Item Sets
body:
https://gyazo.com/f4d7c327d35c52bad8e4db5408d4296d

The Item Sets tab won't show up. :(

replies.body: I wasn't able to find any issues with item lists loading, so I'm curious if you're able to load other panels like your profile?  This may be a result of a connection issue failing to load assets.  Go over our [connection issues](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) guide to troubleshoot this.  Let me know if you have any questions!
